      <title>将工具制造商ISCAR卖给巴菲特的Stef Wertheimer死于98</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/stef-wertheimer-who-sold-toolmaker-iscar-to-buffett-dies-at-98</link>
