      <title>欧洲燃气滑移作为充足的液化天然气流程有助于缓解储存的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/european-gas-slips-as-ample-lng-flows-help-ease-storage-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气在第二天下降了第二天，随着液化天然气的充足供应和温暖的天气缓解该地区的燃料库存，这一年的起步开始了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/european-gas-slips-as-ample-lng-flows-help-ease-storage-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 07:28:06 GMT</pubDate>
